      <akn:section eId="sec_32_510">
        <akn:num>32-510</akn:num>
        <akn:heading>Enforcement by civil action.</akn:heading>
<akn:subsection eId="subsec_32-510_a">
      <akn:num>(a)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>Subject to the provisions in subsection (b) of this section, an employee or the Mayor may bring a civil action against any employer to enforce the provisions of this chapter in any court of competent jurisdiction.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_32-510_b">
      <akn:num>(b)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>No civil action may be commenced more than 1 year after the occurrence or discovery of the alleged violation of this chapter.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_32-510_c">
      <akn:num>(c)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>If a court determines that an employer violated any provision of this chapter, the damages provision prescribed in ยง 32-509(b)(6) and ยง 32-509(b)(7) shall apply.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection>
      </akn:section>
